From: Gemini PDA Mainline Project <noreply@example.com>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 02:00:00 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 23/25] dt-bindings: iommu: mediatek: add MT6797 M4U and SMI

MT6797 has one multimedia M4U connected to seven SMI local arbiters. Add
the three compatibles and a complete port-ID header recovered from the
public vendor port table.

The DT IDs use the standard compact MTK_M4U_ID encoding. They intentionally
do not copy the differently shifted transaction-fault IDs used by the M4U
interrupt registers.

Signed-off-by: Gemini PDA Mainline Project <noreply@example.com>
---
